+ ##deccf1|[[span style="font-family: GmarketSansBold;"]][[size 111%]]P[[/size]][[size 89%]]ATAPHYSICS[[/size]][[size 111%]] D[[/size]][[size 89%]]EPERTMENT[[/size]][[/span]]##
